and making sounds to the rhythm of his heartbeat.&nbsp;

00:04:55.040 --> 00:04:59.440
Lola and Eric enter the house, carrying&nbsp;
Brent with them. Lola goes to her very&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:59.440 --> 00:05:03.920
unsettling and honestly kinda creepy room to&nbsp;
update her scrapbook with a picture of Brent.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:03.920 --> 00:05:08.320
Her father interrupts her when he brings him a&nbsp;
gift: a pink dress and a pair of shoes to match.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:08.320 --> 00:05:12.560
He intends to leave while she changes but she&nbsp;
asks him to stay so he can tell her how she looks,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:12.560 --> 00:05:16.000
which ends up with Eric giving her daughter's&nbsp;
undressed very inappropriate glances.&nbsp;

00:05:16.640 --> 00:05:20.720
They go to the dining room then, where Brent is&nbsp;
waking up to find this strange house decorated to&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:20.720 --> 00:05:25.120
simulate prom. He's been changed into a suit&nbsp;
and tied to a chair in front of table where&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:25.120 --> 00:05:29.920
