sit: Lola, Eric and a woman with a round scar on&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:29.920 --> 00:05:34.800
her forehead that Lola calls Bright Eyes. She&nbsp;
seems to be out of it. Eric leaves his seat to&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:34.800 --> 00:05:39.440
grab Brent so Lola can inject bleach into his&nbsp;
throat to destroy his vocal cords. They smile&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:39.440 --> 00:05:44.320
and tease Brent while doing it, as if it was just&nbsp;
a cute little game. After the injection is done,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:44.320 --> 00:05:49.280
Lola sits on Brent's lap and asks her dad for&nbsp;
a picture. Eric takes it, but asks for a second&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:49.280 --> 00:05:54.720
one together with Bright Eyes. Lola isn't happy&nbsp;
with this idea but accepts anyway. Bright Eyes is&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:54.720 --> 00:05:58.720
dragged onto Brent's lap as well, and she yells&nbsp;
when Lola pulls her hair for the photograph.&nbsp;

00:05:59.440 --> 00:06:03.760
Back in the school, Jamie and Mia drink and smoke&nbsp;
inside the car while listening to heavy metal,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:03.760 --> 00:06:08.880
not joining the party just yet. In contrast to&nbsp;
this, we see Lola's house again, where she and&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:08.880 --> 00:06:12.720
her father are enjoying take-out chicken while&nbsp;
Brent tries to undo the knots of the rope that&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:12.720 --> 00:06:17.120
ties him and Bright Eyes stares at nothing. Lola&nbsp;
finds a wishbone in her chicken and offers it&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:17.120 --> 00:06:21.760
to her dad to make a wish together - Eric wins it&nbsp;
and, even when he swears he's made a wish for her,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:21.760 --> 00:06:27.520
Lola is not amused. Incredibly annoyed, Lola asks&nbsp;
her father who looks prettier: she or Bright Eyes.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:28.080 --> 00:06:32.480
Feeling stuck between a rock and a hard place,&nbsp;
Eric replies that both look pretty, which makes&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:32.480 --> 00:06:37.200
Lola even angrier. She starts force-feeding&nbsp;
chicken and milk to Bright Eyes and, when she&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:37.200 --> 00:06:42.160
realized Brent is watching, decides to try to do&nbsp;
the same to him while using baby talk. Since Brent&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:42.160 --> 00:06:46.160
won't open his mouth for her, Eric stands up and&nbsp;
goes to pick a hammer that he brings back to the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:46.160 --> 00:06:51.760
table as a threat. It works, Brent nods his answer&nbsp;
to Lola's "isn't finger-licking good?" question.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:51.760 --> 00:06:55.040
He also asks for the toilet, and Lola tells&nbsp;
him he'll be allowed to go if he licks her&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:55.040 --> 00:06:59.840
finger first. He obeys, and the not-so-innocent&nbsp;
enjoyment Lola is getting from it causes her&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:59.840 --> 00:07:04.880
jealous dad to stop them. Brent still needs to go&nbsp;
to the toilet (or so he claims, since he's most&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:04.880 --> 00:07:09.760
likely attempting to escape) but Lola, instead of&nbsp;
taking him to the bathroom, chugs a glass of milk&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:09.760 --> 00:07:14.640
and then holds against his now open zipper so he&nbsp;
can pee in it. When Brent doesn't manage to do so,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:14.640 --> 00:07:18.800
he gets threatened again for possibly lying:&nbsp;
he must pee before Lola counts to ten or her&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:18.800 --> 00:07:23.440
dad will nail him to the chair with the hammer he&nbsp;
used to hurt his dog. Brent pulls it off by nine.&nbsp;

00:07:24.160 --> 00:07:28.480
When Lola gets closer and threatens to cut his&nbsp;
member, Brent kicks her back as he finally manages&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:28.480 --> 00:07:33.440
to free his hands from the ropes. He hops his way&nbsp;
out of the house, since his legs are still tied,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:33.440 --> 00:07:36.960
and hides under Eric's truck to have a hidden&nbsp;
place where to cut the remaining rope off with&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:36.960 --> 00:07:40.800
his razor blade. Eric leaves the house&nbsp;
and when he doesn't see Brent around,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:40.800 --> 00:07:44.880
hops inside the truck to give him chase.&nbsp;
Brent rolls away when the engine is turned on,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:44.880 --> 00:07:49.680
believing to be safe now, but Eric pulls back and&nbsp;
the truck lights instantly fall on his victim.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:49.680 --> 00:07:54.240
Brent runs away and climbs a tree where the truck&nbsp;
crashes when Eric goes after him. He walks around&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:54.240 --> 00:07:58.400
the tree without knowing what to do, but Lola&nbsp;
arrives then with a flashlight that allows them&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:58.400 --> 00:08:03.040
to see Brent clearly among vthe branches. They&nbsp;
start throwing rocks at him, laughing and clearly&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:03.040 --> 00:08:07.040
enjoying his pain, until Brent finally falls,&nbsp;
first hitting the truck and then the ground.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:07.600 --> 00:08:12.240
They take him back to the house, where he's tied&nbsp;
to a chair again. Eric proceeds to hammer a knife&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:12.240 --> 00:08:16.880
on Brent's feet as punishment for hitting Lola.&nbsp;
At first Lola just watches, but then she moves&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:16.880 --> 00:08:21.760
to sit on Brent's lap, asking him to cry. But he&nbsp;
doesn't, which makes her frustrated and angry.&nbsp;

00:08:22.480 --> 00:08:25.760
At the same time, Mr Valentine is&nbsp;
investigating the cliff and finds&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:25.760 --> 00:08:29.760
Brent's phone and music player, which he takes&nbsp;
back to Carla, who is waiting in her house with&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:29.760 --> 00:08:33.360
Holly and telling him how Brent believes she&nbsp;
blames him for the accident, but she doesn't.&nbsp;

00:08:34.080 --> 00:08:38.160
Back with Brent, who's been sitted between Eric&nbsp;
and Lola and must endure how she shows him her&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:38.160 --> 00:08:42.160
creepy scrapbook. It's not just an album&nbsp;
of memories, there are pictures of all the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:42.160 --> 00:08:46.560
boys they've kidnapped and tortured for their&nbsp;
fake proms through the years. One in particular&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:46.560 --> 00:08:51.200
calls his attention: Timmy Valentine, the only&nbsp;
one that managed to escape - Brent immediately&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:51.200 --> 00:08:55.040
recognizes him: it's the guy that had stood in&nbsp;
the middle of the road and caused the accident&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:55.040 --> 00:08:59.280
that killed his dad. Anger eats him from&nbsp;
inside: it's all Eric's and Lola's fault.&nbsp;

00:09:00.000 --> 00:09:04.080
Lola tells her dad he's ready to draw on Brent,&nbsp;
and after a quick cut to the school to see that&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:04.080 --> 00:09:08.720
Jaime and Mia still haven't left the car, we see&nbsp;
the results of Lola's "drawing": using a fork,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:08.720 --> 00:09:13.120
she's carved their initials inside a heart on&nbsp;
Brent's chest. Both her and Eric proceed to&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:13.120 --> 00:09:17.840
throw salt at the wound, making Brent scream and&nbsp;
wiggle in pain while they make fun of him for it.&nbsp;

00:09:17.840 --> 00:09:22.880
While Brent is being punished, her mom is still&nbsp;
in their house, waiting for news. Same for Holly,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:22.880 --> 00:09:27.040
who finds the card Brent had prepared for her and&nbsp;
contained the words "I love you" that he owed her.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:27.040 --> 00:09:30.640
And at school, Jaime and Mia finally&nbsp;
decide to leave the car, even if Mia&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:30.640 --> 00:09:35.120
can barely stand, not feeling very well.
It's time for the coronation at Lola's&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:35.120 --> 00:09:40.400
prom. She's the queen, of course, and Brent&nbsp;
is named king. All of them get paper crowns,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:40.400 --> 00:09:45.280
even Eric, who takes a picture of the royal couple&nbsp;
before his daughter decides to play some music.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:45.280 --> 00:09:49.920
It's the actual school dance we see first,&nbsp;
though: Mia and Jaime are slow dancing together,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:49.920 --> 00:09:54.080
and Mia starts touching Jaime's groin, getting&nbsp;
stares from everyone around them and the attention&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:54.080 --> 00:09:58.800
of a teacher, who kicks them out of the party.&nbsp;
